{"tid":889280,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"人行警告明年或現影響巨大金融危機","createTime":"2018-11-04T12:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T09:52:49.000Z","uid":195998,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"105aeac49066bcad5601403ea14ec815601b0da4","tid":889280,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"All in property immediately"},{"pid":"859c777ee17ce97d04c55006b3456318f8327bae","tid":889280,"uid":51294,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T17:18:16.000Z","msg":"人行警告明年或現影響巨大金融危機 政策需更靈活　<br />\n<br />\n2018-11-03 08:17<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人民銀行警告，明年可能出現影響巨大的金融危機。 人民銀行發表金融穩定報告指，已遏止宏觀槓桿率過快上升的趨勢，整體經濟金融風險可控，不會發生系統性風險，但明年全球經濟和金融市場不明朗較大。 內地經濟由高速增長調整至高質量增長過程中，一些「灰犀牛」即較大機會出現，而且影響巨大的金融風險可能會出現，未來政策需要更靈活、協調，亦需要增強金融業抵禦風險和服務實體經濟的能力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌 邊有人咁樣自爆嫁"},{"pid":"c868acd23b8ab9b26cd37aa8709c22b62482de21","tid":889280,"uid":51294,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T17:19:45.000Z","msg":"大陸咁鍾意報喜不報憂，今次咁樣唱淡法係咪真係搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d6472be0a828b6bc46984501de3083b4ecd651","tid":889280,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T17:24:44.000Z","msg":"打定底 可以大裁員？"},{"pid":"7984bd1c9e1266134a645725cface1bb3f9c3d20","tid":889280,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T17:25:48.000Z","msg":"明年,仲有兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d9e54ea312322e4e3f00968953a13122a196f9","tid":889280,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T17:26:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4757ad9e8bb69d95fd2b60f3fe75aedb3c7932c2","tid":889280,"uid":83654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c868acd23b8ab9b26cd37aa8709c22b62482de21","tid":889280,"uid":51294,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T17:19:45.000Z","msg":"大陸咁鍾意報喜不報憂，今次咁